[Sources reported 105 more cases of plague on 20 Oct 2017 than what has come out in the latest WHO report. There have been some irregularities in the numbers before but the number of deaths did climb. We await newer numbers.

With close to 65 percent of the cases diagnosed as pneumonic plague, the case fatality rate of about 8 percent seems quite low. - Mod.LL

